---
title: Double Honey-Mustard Chicken & Creamy Potatoes with Avocado Garden Salad
description: This meal is a true celebration of summer. The chicken is juicy and golden, coated in a sweet and savoury honey-mustard glaze. The creamy potato salad has just the right amount of herby goodness, and the garden salad is vibrant and fresh. Dig in!
